Class CommandManager

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.is25am22new.Client.Commands.CommandManager
public class CommandManager extends Object
Manages all available commands in the game and filters commands based on their applicability to the current game state. The class provides functionality to initialize and maintain the list of commands, as well as retrieve commands available for a specific game context.
